key_21.comment:
No one seems to know exact details
of these sessions anywhere, but the most thorough details available are shown based
on what was written on the PCM tapes and other sources.]

These recordings are of specific interest to completists, but marginal interest to the
casual listener.  To those of us who really missed the band during the year 1975 when
they went into isolation, these recordings give a rare glimpse into the studio where
they were working out the bugs developing tunes to be put on "Blues for Allah".
